===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{taxlink|Salix integra|species}}
#: {{syn|zh|杞柳}}
#* {{zh-x|將 ^仲-子 兮、無 踰 我 里、無 折 我 樹-杞。|I pray you, Master Zhong, Do not come leaping into my hamlet; Do not break my '''willow''' trees.|ref=Shijing}}
# [[wolfberry]]
#: {{syn|zh|枸杞}}
#* {{zh-x|翩-翩 者 鵻{zhuī}、載 飛 載 止、集 于 苞-杞。|Darting and dashing are the turtle-doves; now flying, now stopping; gathering on the lush '''wolfberry-trees'''.|ref=Shijing}}
# a kind of tree
#* {{zh-x|南-山 有 杞，北-山 有 李。|On the southern hills there are '''qi'''-trees; on the northern hills there are plum-trees.|ref=Shijing}}
# a [[small]] [[feudal]] [[state]] ([[w:Qi (Henan)|Qi]]), founded in [[Henan]] during the [[w:Shang Dynasty|Shang Dynasty]]
#: {{zh-x|^杞人憂天|The man of '''Qi''' worrying about the sky}}
#* {{zh-x|杞 小-微，其 事 不足 稱-述。|Qi was too small; its affairs are not worth narrating.|ref=Shiji}}
#* {{zh-x|子曰：「夏-禮，吾 能 言 之，^杞 不足 徵 也；^殷-禮，吾 能 言 之，^宋 不足 徵 也。文獻 不足 故 也，足 則 吾 能 徵 之 矣。」|The Master said, "I could describe the ceremonies of the Xia dynasty, but '''Qi''' cannot sufficiently attest my words. I could describe the ceremonies of the Yin dynasty, but Song cannot sufficiently attest my words. (They cannot do so) because of the insufficiency of their records and wise men. If those were sufficient, I could adduce them in support of my words."|ref=Lunyu}}

